Problem statement
Ninja was very fond of patterns. For a given integer ‘N’, he wants to make the N-Star Rotated Triangle.

Example:
Input: ‘N’ = 3

Output: 

*
**
***
**
*

Code:
public class Solution {
    public static void nStarTriangle(int n) {
        for(int i=1; i<=n; i++){
            for(int j=1; j<=i; j++){
                System.out.print("*");
            }
            System.out.println();
        }
        for(int i=n-1; i>=1; i--){
            for(int j=1; j<=i; j++){
                System.out.print("*");
            }
            System.out.println();
        }
    }
}
